thread.title: Charles Harwood
thread.title_full: Store DJ reviewed by Charles Harwood

author: Charles Harwood
title: Charles Harwood
text: I purchased a set of Audio Technica ATH-M50x monitoring headphones from Store DJ. They had them at a great price and shipping was meant to take about 5 days but they ended up arriving after only 2 days, stoked! The headphones themselves are freaking sweet too. Perfect for use while recording in my home studio and while at work writing code all day. They are so comfortable that I can wear them for a full 8 hour day without even noticing, unlike my old in-ears that they replaced which would start to get a bit uncomfortable after a few hours.
